Note:- 
arr.clone() :
         - Array ka naya object banata hai
         - Same length hoti hai
         - Index-wise values copy hoti hain
         - Original array se different reference hota hai
Arrays.copyOf(originalArray, newLength) :
            - Arrays ek class hai util package ke ander uske ander bahut sari utility method jo as helper method kam krti hai unme se ek ye v hai
            - Naya array object banata hai
            - newLength ke according size set karta hai
            - Original array ke elements index-wise copy karta hai
            - Agar newLength:
                      - chhota hai ‚Üí extra elements cut ho jaate hain
                      - bada hai ‚Üí extra places default values se fill hoti hain
Arrays.copyOfRange(original, from, to) :
                              - range (sub-array) nikalne ke liye use hota hai.
                              - from ‚Üí starting index (inclusive)
                              - to ‚Üí ending index (exclusive)


